title: About
text:
I’m a Data Scientist and Engineer based in London.
Previously, I have worked at coglomerates like World Heath Organisation and University College London. I Started this blog with a purpose to augment my own understanding about new things while helping others learn about them.
I like learning in general whether its related to any field of sciences and constantly work to add up new skills as I face new problems that cannot be accomplished with my current set of techniques. I also really like working with data intensive problems and am constantly in search for new ideas to work on.
